{
  "texts": [
    "The calculation method of the CER and WER is similar.",
    "CER takes the basic unit of Chinese dialect \"character\" as the analysis object and measures the performance of the dialect recognition model by calculating the error level of the character.",
    "The calculation is shown in Eq.",
    "S denotes the dialectal characters replaced in the sentence sequence, D denotes the deleted dialectal characters, I indicates the inserted dialectal characters, and N denotes the total number of Chinese characters.",
    "WER takes Chinese dialect \"words\" as the analysis object and is also one of the critical evaluations for the speech recognition system."
  ]
}